{"type":"node","id":"0","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["精准农业作物推荐器|season"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"用于标识农时季节的文本标签，便于扩展季节差异。该标签可用于影响模型对不同季节因素的处理。","id":"季节标签","node_id":"季节标签"}}
{"type":"node","id":"1","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["精准农业作物推荐器|top_crops"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"包含Top-N作物的推荐结果，每个作物附带评分和预测产量（吨/公顷）。用于为农业决策提供最佳作物种植建议及预期产量评估。","id":"作物推荐与产量预测列表","node_id":"作物推荐与产量预测列表"}}
{"type":"node","id":"2","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["高级农业顾问|price"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"市场价格是指商品在市场上交易的货币价值，通常以货币单位/吨表示或与数据集单位一致，反映经济数据中的价格信息。","id":"市场价格","node_id":"市场价格"}}
{"type":"node","id":"3","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["智能农业决策|decision"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"灌溉决策结果包含归一化特征、灌溉概率（风险分数，包括需水得分）、建议灌溉量及是否建议灌溉，用于指导农田灌溉操作，提高水资源利用效率和作物产量。","id":"灌溉决策结果","node_id":"灌溉决策结果"}}
{"type":"node","id":"4","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["农业助手|result.weather.pest_risk_index"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"病虫害发生风险指数是基于气象数据进行病虫害风险评估的指标，数值范围为0到1，用于预测和管理农业病虫害风险。","id":"病虫害发生风险指数","node_id":"病虫害发生风险指数"}}
{"type":"node","id":"5","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["城市农业产量预测器|predicted_yield","高级农业顾问|Yield"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"作物产量预测值是指预测的作物产量数值，通常以吨/公顷或千克/公顷（如kg/hectare）为单位。该值用于评估作物的预期产量，支持农业生产和管理决策。","id":"作物产量预测值","node_id":"作物产量预测值"}}
{"type":"node","id":"6","labels":["tool"],"properties":{"tool_No":"1014-challengeaci__Tech-Master-5_script.py","output_args":"[{\"output_arg\": \"crop_label\", \"data_type\": \"str\", \"args_description\": \"预测的作物名称（内置 10 类之一）。\", \"resource_category\": \"作物类别预测标签\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"top3\", \"data_type\": \"List[Object{label:str, prob:float}]\", \"args_description\": \"概率最高的前三个作物及其概率。\", \"resource_category\": \"Top-K 作物概率列表\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"probs\", \"data_type\": \"Dict[str, float]\", \"args_description\": \"10 个作物类别的完整概率分布。\", \"resource_category\": \"作物类别概率分布\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"runtime_ms\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"端到端推理耗时（毫秒）。\", \"resource_category\": \"推理性能指标数值\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"device\", \"data_type\": \"str\", \"args_description\": \"实际计算后端，如 'numpy'、'torch/cpu' 或 'torch/cuda'。\", \"resource_category\": \"系统运行环境元数据\"}]","tool_id":"技术专家作物预测器","description":"离线微型作物推荐/预测工具：基于 12 维特征（气温、降雨、N/P/K、季节独热、土壤独热），使用内置线性+Softmax 分类器（预置权重，无需训练/下载），在无网络与无 GPU 的环境下快速输出作物类别及概率分布；优先使用 PyTorch（可用则 CUDA），否则使用 NumPy。","id":"技术专家作物预测器","category":"种","input_args":"[{\"input_arg\": \"temp_c\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"气温（℃），示例范围 10~45。\", \"resource_category\": \"气象传感器数值（气温）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"rainfall_mm\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"降雨量（mm），示例范围 0~500。\", \"resource_category\": \"气象传感器数值（降雨量）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"nitrogen\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"氮含量（kg/ha），示例范围 0~300。\", \"resource_category\": \"土壤养分化验数值（kg/ha）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"phosphorus\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"磷含量（kg/ha），示例范围 0~300。\", \"resource_category\": \"土壤养分化验数值（kg/ha）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"potassium\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"钾含量（kg/ha），示例范围 0~300。\", \"resource_category\": \"土壤养分化验数值（kg/ha）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"season\", \"data_type\": \"int | str\", \"args_description\": \"季节；支持 0/'kharif'，1/'rabi'，2/'yearlong'/'year-round'（内部做独热编码）。\", \"resource_category\": \"农事季节标签（农事日历元数据）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"soil\", \"data_type\": \"int | str\", \"args_description\": \"土壤类型；支持 0/'alluvial'，1/'black'，2/'laterite'，3/'marshy'，4/'red'（内部做独热编码）。\", \"resource_category\": \"土壤类型分类标签（土壤图谱/调查编码）\"}]","input_example":"{\"temp_c\": 28.0, \"rainfall_mm\": 220.0, \"nitrogen\": 90.0, \"phosphorus\": 40.0, \"potassium\": 40.0, \"season\": \"kharif\", \"soil\": \"alluvial\"}","output_example":"{\"crop_label\": \"barley\", \"top3\": [{\"label\": \"barley\", \"prob\": 0.378384}, {\"label\": \"wheat\", \"prob\": 0.196039}, {\"label\": \"cotton\", \"prob\": 0.172531}], \"probs\": {\"maize\": 0.047511, \"cotton\": 0.172531, \"wheat\": 0.196039, \"paddy\": 0.013769, \"barley\": 0.378384, \"sugarcane\": 0.014552, \"jute\": 0.065096, \"sorghum\": 0.043157, \"groundnut\": 0.024973, \"soybean\": 0.043988}, \"runtime_ms\": 28.76, \"device\": \"numpy\"}"}}
{"type":"node","id":"7","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["气候农业指标计算器|gdd_sum"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"积温是指在特定期间内，累计的温度总和（通常以°C·day为单位）。它用于评估作物的生长进程和预测产量，是农业气象和作物模型中的关键指标。","id":"积温","node_id":"积温"}}
{"type":"node","id":"8","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["农业产量与作物推荐器|pred","农业作物产量计算器|pred"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"作物预测结果包括作物类别标签和预估数值（如总产量估计吨数），用于支持农业生产决策和作物种植规划。此类参数可接受单一作物标签或数值形式的预测结果。","id":"作物预测结果","node_id":"作物预测结果"}}
{"type":"node","id":"9","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["智能农业决策|soil_raw","智能农业传感器|soil_adc","智能农业传感器|sensors.soil_adc","智能农业传感器|sensors.soil_moisture_pct","智能农业监测器|humidity_soil"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"土壤湿度参数通过土壤湿度传感器获取的原始ADC读数（10位，范围[0,1023]）或映射得到的百分比值（0~100%）及相对含水量（0~1）表示。该参数可以二维栅格形式呈现，用于监测土壤状况、指导农业灌溉决策、优化水资源管理、提升作物生产效率以及进行土壤健康诊断。在农业模型中，土壤湿度参数用于设定初始湿度状态和初始化随机水分场的强度，是模拟土壤水分动态变化的基础数据。预测结果通常介于0到1之间，用于评估土壤的湿润程度，支持农业环境监测与管理决策，并推荐湿度范围在40~70%。","id":"土壤湿度数据","node_id":"土壤湿度数据"}}
{"type":"node","id":"10","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["农业专家|recommended_categories"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"推荐作物类别是指根据分数阈值筛选出的作物分类列表。该类别集合用于指导后续分析或决策，确保所选作物类别的相关性和可靠性。","id":"推荐作物类别","node_id":"推荐作物类别"}}
{"type":"node","id":"11","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["精准农业作物推荐器|weather"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"包含区/市级湿度（%）与温度（℃）的气象估计数值，用于分析和预测当地的气候条件。","id":"区市级气象数据","node_id":"区市级气象数据"}}
{"type":"node","id":"12","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["农业助手|result.weather.pest_risk_level"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"病害风险等级指标用于评估和分类植物病害的严重程度。通过设定不同的风险等级（低、中、高），包括基于气象因素的风险等级，可以有效指导农业管理决策和病害防控措施的制定。","id":"病害风险等级指标","node_id":"病害风险等级指标"}}
{"type":"node","id":"13","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["农业产量与作物推荐器|ph","城市农业产量预测器|soil_ph","土壤气候作物分类器|ph","农业专家|ph_value","农业作物产量计算器|ph"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"土壤酸碱度（pH值）通过传感器和化验测量，范围3~10，建议在5.5到7.5之间，用于作物推荐、农业管理决策及作物分类特征。此类参数亦用于回归温度推断。该数值可离散为 Acidic、Neutral、Alkaline 并参与规则评分。","id":"土壤酸碱度","node_id":"土壤酸碱度"}}
{"type":"node","id":"14","labels":["tool"],"properties":{"tool_No":"459-vinay72368__Crop-Yield-Prediction-App_script.py","output_args":"[{\"output_arg\": \"prediction\", \"data_type\": \"int\", \"args_description\": \"预测的作物类别编码。\", \"resource_category\": \"作物生长预测结果\"}]","tool_id":"土壤气候作物分类器","description":"该工具用于根据土壤和环境参数预测作物类型，加载预训练的分类器模型并执行预测。","id":"土壤气候作物分类器","category":"种","input_args":"[{\"input_arg\": \"model_file\", \"data_type\": \"str\", \"args_description\": \"存储训练好的分类器 pickle 文件路径。\", \"resource_category\": \"分类器模型文件\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"nitrogen\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"土壤中的氮含量。\", \"resource_category\": \"土壤传感器数值\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"phosphorus\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"土壤中的磷含量。\", \"resource_category\": \"土壤传感器数值\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"potassium\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"土壤中的钾含量。\", \"resource_category\": \"土壤传感器数值\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"temperature\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"环境温度。\", \"resource_category\": \"气象文本数据\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"humidity\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"环境湿度。\", \"resource_category\": \"气象文本数据\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"ph\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"土壤 pH 值。\", \"resource_category\": \"土壤传感器数值\"}]","input_example":"{\"model_file\": \"crop_pred_rand.pkl\", \"nitrogen\": 90.0, \"phosphorus\": 42.0, \"potassium\": 43.0, \"temperature\": 25.2, \"humidity\": 80.0, \"ph\": 6.5}","output_example":"{\"prediction\": 2}"}}
{"type":"node","id":"15","labels":["tool"],"properties":{"tool_No":"354-costantinoschi__AI-Powered-Urban-Agriculture-Optimizer_script.py","output_args":"[{\"output_arg\": \"predicted_yield\", \"data_type\": \"str\", \"args_description\": \"预测的产量（单位：kg/ha）\", \"resource_category\": \"作物生长预测结果\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"recommended_crop\", \"data_type\": \"str\", \"args_description\": \"推荐的作物名称\", \"resource_category\": \"推荐作物名称\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"recommended_month\", \"data_type\": \"str\", \"args_description\": \"推荐的种植月份\", \"resource_category\": \"推荐种植月份\"}]","tool_id":"城市农业产量预测器","description":"该工具用于根据土壤和气候参数（如pH值、氮含量、温度和降水量）预测农作物产量，并推荐合适的作物种类和种植月份。工具内部加载训练好的随机森林模型 `crop_yield_model.pkl`，用于进行产量预测，并通过预测结果推断推荐作物和适宜月份。","id":"城市农业产量预测器","category":"种","input_args":"[{\"input_arg\": \"soil_ph\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"土壤的pH值（范围建议在5.5到7.5之间）\", \"resource_category\": \"土壤pH值\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"nitrogen\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"土壤中氮含量（通常由咖啡渣贡献）\", \"resource_category\": \"土壤氮含量\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"temperature\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"当前或预计的气温（摄氏度）\", \"resource_category\": \"气温数据\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"rainfall\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"当前或预计的降水量（毫米）\", \"resource_category\": \"降水量数据\"}]","input_example":"{\"soil_ph\": 6.8, \"nitrogen\": 30.0, \"temperature\": 23.0, \"rainfall\": 110.0}","output_example":"{\"predicted_yield\": \"210.45 kg/ha\", \"recommended_crop\": \"Tomatoes\", \"recommended_month\": \"April\"}"}}
{"type":"node","id":"16","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["气候农业指标计算器|last_spi_z"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"SPI-like z分数指标是一种基于降水数据计算的标准化干湿状况指标，用于评估特定时期的干旱或湿润程度。","id":"SPI-like z分数指标","node_id":"SPI-like z分数指标"}}
{"type":"node","id":"17","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["农业助手|result.image.brown_ratio"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"褐斑像素占比是指图像中表现褐斑的像素所占的比例，用于评估植物健康状况。通过分析褐斑像素比例，可以检测植物潜在的病害或生长问题。","id":"褐斑像素占比","node_id":"褐斑像素占比"}}
{"type":"node","id":"18","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["智能农业传感器|sensors.dew_point_c"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"露点温度是通过Magnus公式估算得出的环境监测指标，用于衡量空气中水汽含量和湿度水平，广泛应用于气象分析。","id":"露点温度","node_id":"露点温度"}}
{"type":"node","id":"19","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["技术专家作物预测器|top3","农业专家|recommended_plants"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"Top-K 作物概率列表包含模型预测中每张图片的概率最高的K个作物或杂草类别及其对应的概率值，或按适宜度排序的作物名称列表，用于展示作物种植推荐的概率分布或排名。","id":"Top-K 作物概率列表","node_id":"Top-K 作物概率列表"}}
{"type":"node","id":"20","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["城市农业产量预测器|recommended_month"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"推荐种植月份是基于气候和土壤等因素，系统提供的最佳种植时间建议，旨在优化种植计划，提高作物产量和质量。","id":"推荐种植月份","node_id":"推荐种植月份"}}
{"type":"node","id":"21","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["技术专家作物预测器|crop_label"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"预测的作物名称标签，用于表示作物的分类结果，包含内置的10类之一，包括蔬菜类别。","id":"作物分类标签","node_id":"作物分类标签"}}
{"type":"node","id":"22","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["农业助手|image_result"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"包含来自图像检测的中间结果，通常以JSON格式存储，用于summary模式的分析和汇总。","id":"图像检测中间结果","node_id":"图像检测中间结果"}}
{"type":"node","id":"24","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["气候农业指标计算器|advisory"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"基于WRSI与GDD的种植适宜性建议结果。提供“适宜”或“关注”两种建议，用于指导农业生产决策。","id":"种植适宜性建议","node_id":"种植适宜性建议"}}
{"type":"node","id":"25","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["农业专家|drainage"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"田块排水条件表示田地的排水状况，通常分为'Poor'、'Moderate'、'Well'等等级。该参数经过归一化处理后，用于模型评分以评估农田的水分管理效果。","id":"田块排水条件","node_id":"田块排水条件"}}
{"type":"node","id":"26","labels":["tool"],"properties":{"tool_No":"SENS-0262","output_args":"[{\"output_arg\": \"湿度数据\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"由传感器/成像/便携化学/设备遥测采集并回传的“湿度数据”。单位：%\", \"resource_category\": \"传感器观测数据\"}]","tool_id":"湿度传感器","description":"从现场传感器/设备读取“湿度数据”即时值；输入为空，返回原样数据。依据节点描述：湿度数据，表示环境湿度的百分比，影响食品的保鲜天数。用于监控储存环境的湿度变化。","id":"湿度传感器","category":"采","input_args":"[]","input_example":"{}","output_example":"{\"湿度数据\": 63.2}"}}
