{"type":"relationship","id":"1152921504606846976","label":"input","start":{"id":"0","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["精准农业作物推荐器|season"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"用于标识农时季节的文本标签，便于扩展季节差异。该标签可用于影响模型对不同季节因素的处理。","id":"季节标签","node_id":"季节标签"}},"end":{"id":"37","labels":["tool"],"properties":{"tool_No":"495-daksha-aeer__Precision-Agriculture_script.py","output_args":"[{\"output_arg\": \"soil_type\", \"data_type\": \"str\", \"args_description\": \"预测的土壤类型（Alluvial/Black/Loam/Red）。\", \"resource_category\": \"土壤类型分类标签\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"avg_rainfall_cm\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"根据州/省生成的确定性平均降雨量（cm）。\", \"resource_category\": \"地区平均降雨估计数值\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"weather\", \"data_type\": \"{humidity: float, temperature_c: float}\", \"args_description\": \"区/市对应的湿度（%）与温度（℃）估计。\", \"resource_category\": \"区/市级气象估计数值\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"npk\", \"data_type\": \"{N: float, P: float, K: float}\", \"args_description\": \"按土壤类型给出的N/P/K建议值（在建议范围内采样）。\", \"resource_category\": \"施肥养分建议数值（N/P/K）\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"top_crops\", \"data_type\": \"List[{crop: str, score: float, pred_yield_t_ha: float}]\", \"args_description\": \"Top-N作物推荐及其条件评分与产量估计（t/ha）。\", \"resource_category\": \"作物推荐与产量估计结果（t/ha）\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"runtime_ms\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"端到端推理总耗时（毫秒）。\", \"resource_category\": \"运行元信息（无外部数据）\"}]","tool_id":"精准农业作物推荐器","description":"在离线、无外部权重与无GPU环境下，将土壤图像→土壤类型→（地区平均降雨/区县级温湿度/NPK建议）→作物Top-N推荐与产量估计（t/ha）串联为可复现的小工具：采用启发式/可选极小torch前向进行土壤分类，使用确定性伪随机映射生成天气与降雨，基于作物知识表进行规则打分并给出产量估计；仅含推理与评估，无训练与联网依赖。","id":"精准农业作物推荐器","category":"知","input_args":"[{\"input_arg\": \"soil_image\", \"data_type\": \"str | PIL.Image.Image | numpy.ndarray\", \"args_description\": \"土壤图像输入，内部统一为32×32的RGB数组用于启发式/极小前向分类。\", \"resource_category\": \"农田土壤图像\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"state\", \"data_type\": \"str\", \"args_description\": \"州/省名称，用于确定性估计该地区的平均降雨量（cm）。\", \"resource_category\": \"农业地理区划文本数据（州/省名）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"district\", \"data_type\": \"str\", \"args_description\": \"区/市名称，用于确定性估计当地湿度与气温。\", \"resource_category\": \"农业地理区划文本数据（区/市名）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"season\", \"data_type\": \"str\", \"args_description\": \"农时季节标签（接口保留，便于扩展季节差异）。\", \"resource_category\": \"农时季节文本标签\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"area\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"种植面积（ha），产量以t/ha输出，可据此换算总产量。\", \"resource_category\": \"农田地块面积数值（公顷）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"n\", \"data_type\": \"int\", \"args_description\": \"返回的作物推荐Top-N数量。\", \"resource_category\": \"工具配置参数（无外部数据）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"use_torch\", \"data_type\": \"bool\", \"args_description\": \"是否启用极小torch前向分支（若环境可用）。\", \"resource_category\": \"工具运行开关（无外部数据）\"}]","input_example":"{\"soil_image\": \"np.ndarray(32x32x3, R=180, G=80, B=60)\", \"state\": \"Rajasthan\", \"district\": \"Kota\", \"season\": \"Whole Year\", \"area\": 1.0, \"n\": 3, \"use_torch\": false}","output_example":"{\"soil_type\": \"Black\", \"avg_rainfall_cm\": 5.137891798259901, \"weather\": {\"humidity\": 58.99945599645727, \"temperature_c\": 20.67360674032784}, \"npk\": {\"N\": 0.20976270078546494, \"P\": 0.027151893663724194, \"K\": 0.22055267521432875}, \"top_crops\": [{\"crop\": \"Cotton\", \"score\": 0.719579356292448, \"pred_yield_t_ha\": 1.5980971365305627}, {\"crop\": \"Millets\", \"score\": 0.689121336511028, \"pred_yield_t_ha\": 1.3134728019066169}, {\"crop\": \"Sugarcane\", \"score\": 0.669968232844093, \"pred_yield_t_ha\": 6.075911051963461}], \"runtime_ms\": 0.72}"}}}
{"type":"relationship","id":"1152921504606846978","label":"input","start":{"id":"2","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["高级农业顾问|price"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"市场价格是指商品在市场上交易的货币价值，通常以货币单位/吨表示或与数据集单位一致，反映经济数据中的价格信息。","id":"市场价格","node_id":"市场价格"}},"end":{"id":"66","labels":["tool"],"properties":{"tool_No":"1063-Hkarthik13__sustainable-agriculture_script.py","output_args":"[{\"output_arg\": \"Crop\", \"data_type\": \"str\", \"args_description\": \"作物名称\", \"resource_category\": \"作物信息\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"Yield\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"预测产量（吨/公顷）\", \"resource_category\": \"作物生长预测结果\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"Profit\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"预计盈利（price*Yield - cost）\", \"resource_category\": \"经济评估\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"Sustainability\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"可持续性评分（0–100）\", \"resource_category\": \"可持续性评估\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"Planting Time\", \"data_type\": \"str\", \"args_description\": \"推荐种植季节\", \"resource_category\": \"种植时间建议\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"Advice\", \"data_type\": \"list\", \"args_description\": \"针对各环境参数的调控建议\", \"resource_category\": \"作物管理建议\"}]","tool_id":"高级农业顾问","description":"该工具基于环境条件（soil pH、soil moisture、temperature、rainfall）和经济因素（price、cost），使用随机森林回归模型预测四种主要作物（Wheat, Soybean, Corn, Rice）的产量，并根据每种作物的最优生长参数范围计算可持续性评分、估算预计盈利，最后给出最佳种植季节和具体调控建议。","id":"高级农业顾问","category":"种","input_args":"[{\"input_arg\": \"ph\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"土壤 pH 值\", \"resource_category\": \"土壤传感器数值\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"moisture\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"土壤水分百分比\", \"resource_category\": \"土壤传感器数值\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"temp\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"平均温度（摄氏度）\", \"resource_category\": \"气象文本数据\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"rain\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"季节降雨量（毫米）\", \"resource_category\": \"气象文本数据\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"loc\", \"data_type\": \"str\", \"args_d