小时降雨量（mm）\", \"resource_category\": \"气象数值（24h累计降雨量，mm）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"image_result\", \"data_type\": \"字典(Dict[str,Any])\", \"args_description\": \"来自图像检测的中间结果（用于summary模式）\", \"resource_category\": \"上游图像健康检测结果（JSON）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"weather_result\", \"data_type\": \"字典(Dict[str,Any])\", \"args_description\": \"来自气象评估的中间结果（用于summary模式）\", \"resource_category\": \"上游气象评估结果（JSON）\"}]","input_example":"{\"mode\": \"weather\", \"temperature_c\": 28.5, \"humidity_pct\": 60.0, \"wind_mps\": 2.3, \"rain_mm_24h\": 0.0}","output_example":"{\"mode\": \"weather\", \"result\": {\"dryness_index\": 0.662, \"pest_risk_index\": 0.753, \"dryness_level\": \"高\", \"pest_risk_level\": \"高\", \"advice\": \"注意灌溉，优先早晚小水勤浇；留意病虫高发（温湿度偏高），可设置诱捕板并加强巡查\"}, \"device\": \"cpu\", \"runtime_ms\": 25.4}"}}}
{"type":"relationship","id":"1152921504606847001","label":"input","start":{"id":"25","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["农业专家|drainage"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"田块排水条件表示田地的排水状况，通常分为'Poor'、'Moderate'、'Well'等等级。该参数经过归一化处理后，用于模型评分以评估农田的水分管理效果。","id":"田块排水条件","node_id":"田块排水条件"}},"end":{"id":"30","labels":["tool"],"properties":{"tool_No":"272-ZermatAbdenour__Agriculture-Expert-System_script.py","output_args":"[{\"output_arg\": \"inputs\", \"data_type\": \"Dict[str, Any]\", \"args_description\": \"对本次调用的原始输入进行回显，便于审计与复现。\", \"resource_category\": \"原始输入回显元数据\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"classes\", \"data_type\": \"Dict[str, str]\", \"args_description\": \"pH、温度、降水与排水的离散等级（如 Neutral/Moderate/High/Well）。\", \"resource_category\": \"指标离散等级字典\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"category_scores\", \"data_type\": \"List[Tuple[str, float]]\", \"args_description\": \"六大作物类别的评分（按分数降序排列）。\", \"resource_category\": \"作物类别评分列表\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"recommended_categories\", \"data_type\": \"List[str]\", \"args_description\": \"分数达到阈值的候选作物类别名称。\", \"resource_category\": \"候选作物类别集合\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"recommended_plants\", \"data_type\": \"List[str]\", \"args_description\": \"根据类别分数与细粒度启发式从可用清单中选出的具体作物名（Top-K）。\", \"resource_category\": \"推荐具体作物名称列表\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"runtime_ms\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"端到端推理耗时（毫秒）。\", \"resource_category\": \"运行时性能指标\"}]","tool_id":"农业专家","description":"基于启发式规则的离线农业专家系统：根据土壤pH、环境温度、降水量、排水条件与养分元素清单对六类作物（Grains/Cruciferous/Leafy/Root/Legumes/Nightshade）进行评分，返回推荐类别与具体作物；可读取仓库Database作物清单或使用内置兜底；无训练与联网依赖，CPU毫秒级完成，支持可复现的随机种子与耗时日志。","id":"农业专家","category":"知","input_args":"[{\"input_arg\": \"ph_value\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"土壤酸碱度数值，用于离散为 Acidic/Neutral/Alkaline 并参与规则评分。\", \"resource_category\": \"土壤酸碱度传感器/化验数值（pH）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"temperature_c\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"环境温度（摄氏度），离散为 Low/Moderate/High 影响各作物类别倾向。\", \"resource_category\": \"气象温度观测数据（℃）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"precipitation_mm\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"一定时间窗口内降水量（毫米），离散为 Low/Moderate/High 参与规则评分。\", \"resource_category\": \"气象降水量记录（mm）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"drainage\", \"data_type\": \"str\", \"args_description\": \"田块排水条件，支持 'Poor'/'Moderate'/'Well'（大小写不敏感），将被归一化后用于评分。\", \"resource_category\": \"田块排水状况调查/文本标注\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"nutrients\", \"data_type\": \"List[str]\", \"args_description\": \"养分元素名称列表（如 Nitrogen/Phosphorus/Potassium/Calcium/Sulfur），用于全局或定向加分。\", \"resource_category\": \"施肥配方/农资清单文本（养分元素名）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"topk\", \"data_type\": \"int\", \"args_description\": \"返回的推荐具体作物数量上限。\", \"resource_category\": \"算法控制参数（结果裁剪）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"score_threshold\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"筛选推荐类别/作物的最低分阈值。\", \"resource_category\": \"算法控制参数（阈值设置）\"}]","input_example":"{\"ph_value\": 6.8, \"temperature_c\": 22.0, \"precipitation_mm\": 60.0, \"drainage\": \"Moderate\", \"nutrients\": [\"Nitrogen\", \"Phosphorus\", \"Potassium\"], \"topk\": 5, \"score_threshold\": 1.5}","output_example":"{\"inputs\": {\"pH\": 6.8, \"temperature_c\": 22.0, \"precipitation_mm\": 60.0, \"drainage\": \"Moderate\", \"nutrients\": [\"Nitrogen\", \"Phosphorus\", \"Potassium\"]}, \"classes\": {\"PH\": \"Neutral\", \"Temperature\": \"Moderate\", \"Precipitation\": \"Moderate\", \"Drainage\": \"Moderate\"}, \"category_scores\": [[\"Legumes\", 5.5], [\"LeafyGreens\", 3.5], [\"Grains\", 1.5], [\"RootVegetables\", 1.5], [\"NightshadeVegetables\", 1.5], [\"CruciferousVegetables\", 0.5]], \"recommended_categories\": [\"Legumes\", \"LeafyGreens\", \"Grains\", \"RootVegetables\", \"NightshadeVegetables\"], \"recommended_plants\": [\"Soybeans\", \"Lettuce\", \"Spinach\", \"Potatoes\", \"Rice\"], \"runtime_ms\": 0.06}"}}}
{"type":"relationship","id":"1152922604118474778","label":"output","start":{"id":"26","labels":["tool"],"properties":{"tool_No":"SENS-0262","output_args":"[{\"output_arg\": \"湿度数据\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"由传感器/成像/便携化学/设备遥测采集并回传的“湿度数据”。单位：%\", \"resource_category\": \"传感器观测数据\"}]","tool_id":"湿度传感器","description":"从现场传感器/设备读取“湿度数据”即时值；输入为空，返回原样数据。依据节点描述：湿度数据，表示环境湿度的百分比，影响食品的保鲜天数。用于监控储存环境的湿度变化。","id":"湿度传感器","category":"采","input_args":"[]","input_example":"{}","output_example":"{\"湿度数据\": 63.2}"}},"end":{"id":"62","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["农业产量与作物推荐器|humidity","农业助手|humidity_pct","智能农业决策|rel_hum","智能农业传感器|humid_pct","智能农业传感器|sensors.humidity_pct","农业作物产量计算器|humidity","智能农业监测器|humidity_air","湿度传感器|湿度数据","土壤气候作物分类器|humidity"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"相对湿度指标表示空气中水蒸气含量与饱和水蒸气含量的比值，以百分比（0~100%）形式表达。该数据通过田间湿度传感器（如DHT22）或环境监测系统获取，当参数缺失时使用内部模拟的固定值。相对湿度作为关键的气象数据，广泛应用于农业管理和决策，包括作物推荐、灌溉指导、温度推断，以及分析气候条件、预测天气变化和研究生态系统的水分状态。此外，湿度数据还用于监控储存环境的湿度变化，影响食品的保鲜天数。因此，相对湿度指标在农业生产、环境评估和食品储存等多个领域具有重要的应用价值。","id":"湿度","node_id":"湿度"}}}
