est_risk_level\", \"data_type\": \"字符串（低/中/高）\", \"args_description\": \"病虫害风险等级\", \"resource_category\": \"气象风险等级标签（病虫害）\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"result.weather.advice\", \"data_type\": \"字符串\", \"args_description\": \"基于风险的田间管理建议（中文）\", \"resource_category\": \"田间管理建议文本\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"result.summary.text\", \"data_type\": \"字符串\", \"args_description\": \"图像与气象结果的综合中文总结\", \"resource_category\": \"综合中文总结文本（可用于TTS/展示）\"}]","tool_id":"农业助手","description":"离线单入口农业助手：支持农田图像健康检测（黄化/褐斑占比）、基于本地气象数值的干旱与病虫害风险评估，并生成中文总结；CPU可运行、无网络/无GPU依赖，提供阈值与设备降级。","id":"农业助手","category":"管","input_args":"[{\"input_arg\": \"mode\", \"data_type\": \"字符串\", \"args_description\": \"运行模式选择：image / weather / summary / demo\", \"resource_category\": \"运行控制参数\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"image_array\", \"data_type\": \"NumPy数组(uint8)[H,W,3]\", \"args_description\": \"输入待检测的RGB农田图像数组\", \"resource_category\": \"农田图像（RGB三通道，uint8）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"image_path\", \"data_type\": \"字符串（文件路径）\", \"args_description\": \"本地图像文件路径；若提供将尝试读取图像\", \"resource_category\": \"本地图像文件路径（农田实拍）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"yellow_hsv_lo\", \"data_type\": \"整数三元组(tuple[int,int,int])\", \"args_description\": \"黄色阈值下界（HSV）\", \"resource_category\": \"算法配置参数（HSV颜色阈值-黄）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"yellow_hsv_hi\", \"data_type\": \"整数三元组(tuple[int,int,int])\", \"args_description\": \"黄色阈值上界（HSV）\", \"resource_category\": \"算法配置参数（HSV颜色阈值-黄）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"brown_hsv_lo\", \"data_type\": \"整数三元组(tuple[int,int,int])\", \"args_description\": \"褐色阈值下界（HSV）\", \"resource_category\": \"算法配置参数（HSV颜色阈值-褐）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"brown_hsv_hi\", \"data_type\": \"整数三元组(tuple[int,int,int])\", \"args_description\": \"褐色阈值上界（HSV）\", \"resource_category\": \"算法配置参数（HSV颜色阈值-褐）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"temperature_c\", \"data_type\": \"浮点数\", \"args_description\": \"气温（°C）\", \"resource_category\": \"气象数值（气温，°C）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"humidity_pct\", \"data_type\": \"浮点数\", \"args_description\": \"相对湿度（0~100%）\", \"resource_category\": \"气象数值（相对湿度，%）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"wind_mps\", \"data_type\": \"浮点数\", \"args_description\": \"风速（m/s）\", \"resource_category\": \"气象数值（风速，m/s）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"rain_mm_24h\", \"data_type\": \"浮点数\", \"args_description\": \"过去24小时降雨量（mm）\", \"resource_category\": \"气象数值（24h累计降雨量，mm）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"image_result\", \"data_type\": \"字典(Dict[str,Any])\", \"args_description\": \"来自图像检测的中间结果（用于summary模式）\", \"resource_category\": \"上游图像健康检测结果（JSON）\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"weather_result\", \"data_type\": \"字典(Dict[str,Any])\", \"args_description\": \"来自气象评估的中间结果（用于summary模式）\", \"resource_category\": \"上游气象评估结果（JSON）\"}]","input_example":"{\"mode\": \"weather\", \"temperature_c\": 28.5, \"humidity_pct\": 60.0, \"wind_mps\": 2.3, \"rain_mm_24h\": 0.0}","output_example":"{\"mode\": \"weather\", \"result\": {\"dryness_index\": 0.662, \"pest_risk_index\": 0.753, \"dryness_level\": \"高\", \"pest_risk_level\": \"高\", \"advice\": \"注意灌溉，优先早晚小水勤浇；留意病虫高发（温湿度偏高），可设置诱捕板并加强巡查\"}, \"device\": \"cpu\", \"runtime_ms\": 25.4}"}}}
{"type":"relationship","id":"1166432303488958533","label":"input","start":{"id":"69","labels":["recourse"],"properties":{"node_args":["智能农业监测器|temperature","智能农业传感器|temp_c","高级农业顾问|temp","气温传感器|温度"],"node_type":"data","node_description":"温度指标参数表示在特定时间内的平均环境空气温度，通常以摄氏度或华氏度为单位。该参数通过传感器（如DHT22）采集温度数据，或在数据缺失时通过固定模拟值或随机种子生成可复现的数值。温度指标是气候分析和农业生产决策的关键输入，用于预测作物生长条件、调整管理策略以及评估热量条件对作物适宜性的影响。基于环境与土壤特征（如湿度、pH值）的回归模型可用于推断温度变化趋势，进一步支持作物生长过程中的温度分析与预测。此外，温度指标还应用于气象分析和天气预报，以提供准确的温度感知信息。","id":"气温","node_id":"气温"}},"end":{"id":"66","labels":["tool"],"properties":{"tool_No":"1063-Hkarthik13__sustainable-agriculture_script.py","output_args":"[{\"output_arg\": \"Crop\", \"data_type\": \"str\", \"args_description\": \"作物名称\", \"resource_category\": \"作物信息\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"Yield\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"预测产量（吨/公顷）\", \"resource_category\": \"作物生长预测结果\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"Profit\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"预计盈利（price*Yield - cost）\", \"resource_category\": \"经济评估\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"Sustainability\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"可持续性评分（0–100）\", \"resource_category\": \"可持续性评估\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"Planting Time\", \"data_type\": \"str\", \"args_description\": \"推荐种植季节\", \"resource_category\": \"种植时间建议\"}, {\"output_arg\": \"Advice\", \"data_type\": \"list\", \"args_description\": \"针对各环境参数的调控建议\", \"resource_category\": \"作物管理建议\"}]","tool_id":"高级农业顾问","description":"该工具基于环境条件（soil pH、soil moisture、temperature、rainfall）和经济因素（price、cost），使用随机森林回归模型预测四种主要作物（Wheat, Soybean, Corn, Rice）的产量，并根据每种作物的最优生长参数范围计算可持续性评分、估算预计盈利，最后给出最佳种植季节和具体调控建议。","id":"高级农业顾问","category":"种","input_args":"[{\"input_arg\": \"ph\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"土壤 pH 值\", \"resource_category\": \"土壤传感器数值\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"moisture\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"土壤水分百分比\", \"resource_category\": \"土壤传感器数值\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"temp\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"平均温度（摄氏度）\", \"resource_category\": \"气象文本数据\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"rain\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"季节降雨量（毫米）\", \"resource_category\": \"气象文本数据\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"loc\", \"data_type\": \"str\", \"args_description\": \"地点信息（用于判断半球，如 'Northern India'）\", \"resource_category\": \"地理位置信息\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"price\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"市场价格（单位：货币/吨 或 与数据集单位一致）\", \"resource_category\": \"经济数据\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"cost\", \"data_type\": \"float\", \"args_description\": \"种植成本（单位：与 price 相同）\", \"resource_category\": \"经济数据\"}, {\"input_arg\": \"data_file\", \"data_type\": \"str\", \"args_description\": \"数据集路径，需包含字段 Soil_pH, Soil_Moisture, Temperature_C, Rainfall_mm, Crop_Type, Crop_Yield_ton\", \"resource_category\": \"农田历史数据\"}]","input_example":"{\"ph\": 6.8, \"moisture\": 32.0, \"temp\": 26.0, \"rain\": 175.0, \"loc\": \"Northern India\", \"price\": 20000.0, \"cost\": 5000.0, \"data_file\": \"farmer_advisor_dataset.csv\"}","output_example":"[{\"Crop\": \"Soybean\", \"Yield\": 3.45, \"Profit\": 61400.0, \"Sustainability\": 92.5, \"Planting Time\": \"Kharif (Jun-Jul)\", \"Advice\": [\"✅ pH (6.8) 处于最佳范围 6.2–7.0。\", \"⚠️ Moisture (32.0) 超出最佳范围 25–40，建议调整。\", \"✅ Temp (26.0) 处于最佳范围 20–30。\", \"✅ Rain (175.0) 处于最佳范围 100–200。\"]}]"}}}
